data.description: Lovely updated Ranch home on the desirable Northside of Evansville. New extended front porch invites you to relax with your morning cup of coffee. This charming home has been professionally painted, new LVP flooring throughout, and has an easy flow from room to room. The living room has a new gas fireplace perfect for cozy winter evenings with your loved ones. The large eat-in kitchen has updated cabinetry, newer appliances, and a food pantry. The upper level has three spacious bedrooms and a full bath featuring a walk-in shower and new vanity. The full finished basement has so much room for recreational use, a fun home movie theater, and a workshop space. There is an additional flex space which could be used as a 4th bedroom or an exercise room which features a large walk-in closet and built-in TV. New furnace (2021), privacy fence (2019), extended open porch (2021), new flooring (2019, 2023), ring security system included. Open patio with pergola in fenced-in backyard perfect for back yard fires on these chilly evenings. 2.5 detached garage has ample amount of storage space. You do not want to miss out on this Northside beauty!
